snippet.title: New 2025 Rhythm Game - 60 BPM is out now on Steam!!! Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get 60 BPM now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3222860/60_BPM

60 Beats per Minute is the rhythm of a healthy heart at rest, but be ready to speed it up, chill out, and enjoy the music with 60 BPM!
As a rhythm game, you play by tapping on-beat with the music by following sound and visual cues, with cute copilots and powerful boosters eagerly to assist along your journey.
